==English==

===Etymology===
'''[[ice]]''' + '''[[box]]''', as before electric [[refrigeration]] it was literally a box loaded with ice to keep things cold

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-es}}

# A box containing ice, used to keep food cold.
# (''British'') A compartment in a [[refrigerator]] that is colder than the rest of the refrigerator and is used as a [[freezer]].
# (''US'') A [[refrigerator]].

